    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk i don't think it's just a schedule. it's too consistent. like if i'm having a bad night the temperature drop happens almost immediately. plus my fridge has a camera in it for the grocery app... wouldn't it be easy for those things to be linked to an external server that's analyzing how i'm acting? i'm not saying it's definitely happening but the technical possibility is there right?",
